query:
select bio.biomarker_description, bftu.actual_use
from biomarker as bio
    join biomarker_fda as bf on bio.id = bf.id
    join biomarker_fda_test as bft on bf.test_submission = bft.test_submission and bf.test_trade_name = bft.test_trade_name
    join biomarker_fda_test_use as bftu on bft.test_submission = bftu.test_submission and bft.test_trade_name = bftu.test_trade_name
    join disease as d on bft.doid = d.id
    join disease_mutation as dm on d.id = dm.doid
where d.name = 'colorectal cancer' and dm.chromosome_id = '4'
question: Show all the information about biomarkers and their actual use for biomarkers related to colorectal cancer with mutations in the chromosome with id 4

query:
select bio.biomarker_description, d.name
from biomarker as bio
    join biomarker_fda as bf on bio.id = bf.id
    join biomarker_fda_test as bft on bf.test_submission = bft.test_submission and bf.test_trade_name = bft.test_trade_name
    join disease as d on bft.doid = d.id
    join disease_mutation as dm on d.id = dm.doid

query:
select bio.biomarker_description, muci.uniprotkb_canonical_ac
from biomarker as bio
    join biomarker_fda as bf on bio.id = bf.id
    join biomarker_fda_test as bft on bf.test_submission = bft.test_submission and bf.test_trade_name = bft.test_trade_name
    join disease as d on bft.doid = d.id
    join disease_mutation as dm on d.id = dm.doid
    join map_protein_disease_mutation as mpdm on dm.ensembl_transcript_id = mpdm.ensembl_transcript_id
    join map_uniprot_canonical_id as muci on mpdm.uniprotkb_ac = muci.uniprotkb_ac
question: Show all the information about biomarkers and the uniprot canonical ids of their mutations
